# ResBlaster

![PYPI](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/ResBlaster)
![Static Badge](https://img.shields.io/badge/OS-_Windows_%7C_Mac_%7C_Linux-steelblue)

```
 ____           ____  _           _
|  _ \ ___  ___| __ )| | __ _ ___| |_ ___ _ __
